  "title": "Group Leader",
  "description": "<p><strong>Required Skills:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Accounting audit response</li>\n  <li>Monthly financial closing</li>\n  <li>Head office reporting</li>\n  <li>Head office questionnaire responses</li>\n  <li>Document preparation (investments)</li>\n  <li>Investment and financing</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Japanese is required to communicate with the company's Japanese-speaking team members in Japan and to review internal documents written in Japanese</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Specific Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Checking and finalizing monthly financial closing</li>\n  <li>Preparing monthly reports (for head office)</li>\n  <li>Preparing annual financial closing</li>\n  <li>Responding to accounting audits</li>\n  <li>Corporate tax calculation</li>\n  <li>Checking and submitting GST filings</li>\n  <li>Responding to survey requests from head office (on key metrics)</li>\n  <li>Budget formulation (consolidation)</li>\n  <li>Budget vs. actual management</li>\n  <li>Preparing board of directors and shareholder meeting materials (in Japanese)</li>\n  <li>Valuation support (approximate), able to create discounted cash flow (DCF) models</li>\n  <li>Preparing investment and financing materials (for head office)</li>\n  <li>Reviewing business investments</li>\n  <li>Team management (supervising 3 subordinates)</li>\n</ul>",
